  "detailed_description": "<strong>Big Hit VR Baseball</strong> is a pick-up-and-play mix of accurate baseball simulation and arcade-y action. Do you have what it takes to hit a big league fastball? Step up to the plate!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Baseballs move using the real physics of baseball, including spin<br></li><li>Face off against <strong>Fastballs</strong>, <strong>Sinkers</strong>, <strong>Curveballs</strong>, <strong>Changeups</strong>, <strong>Sliders</strong>, and <strong>Cutters</strong><br></li><li>Hone your swing in <strong>Batting Practice </strong>or go for the fences in <strong>Home Run Contest</strong>. More batting challenges coming soon.<br></li><li>Fun for <strong>any age</strong> or <strong>ability</strong>: Increase the baseball size, slow it down, or juice it to hit massive home runs!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Big Hit VR Baseball</strong> is a pick-up-and-play mix of accurate baseball simulation and arcade-y action. Do you have what it takes to hit a big league fastball? Step up to the plate!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Baseballs move using the real physics of baseball, including spin<br></li><li>Face off against <strong>Fastballs</strong>, <strong>Sinkers</strong>, <strong>Curveballs</strong>, <strong>Changeups</strong>, <strong>Sliders</strong>, and <strong>Cutters</strong><br></li><li>Hone your swing in <strong>Batting Practice </strong>or go for the fences in <strong>Home Run Contest</strong>. More batting challenges coming soon.<br></li><li>Fun for <strong>any age</strong> or <strong>ability</strong>: Increase the baseball size, slow it down, or juice it to hit massive home runs!</li></ul>",
